      <text xml:space="preserve">{{Refimprove|date=August 2009}}
{{Infobox book | &lt;!-- See [[Wikipedia:WikiProject Novels]] or [[Wikipedia:WikiProject Books]] --&gt;
| name          = Crash
| title_orig    = 
