*{{cite book| author=McCabe, W., Smith, J. and Harriott, P.|edition=7th |title=[[Unit Operations of Chemical Engineering]]|publisher=McGraw Hill|location=|year=2004|isbn=0-07-284823-5}}
*{{cite book|author= Seader, J. D., and Henley, Ernest J.|title=Separation Process Principles|publisher=Wiley| location=New York|year=1998|isbn=0-471-58626-9}}
* [[John Servos|Servos, John W.]], [http://books.google.com/books?id=1UZjU2WfLAoC&amp;printsec=frontcover ''Physical chemistry from Ostwald to Pauling : the making of a science in America''], Princeton, N.J. : Princeton University Press, 1990. ISBN 0691085668

